Skill name: Tsunami
Cost: Variable
Guild level: 15
Syntax: tsunami <target> <sps you want to invest>

Description:
This is the main, big mighty skill of the Samurai. And a bit
complex to explain, too. This is the only skill (that I know of)
that allows you to invest how many sp's you want to spend on it.
You would assume, the more you spend the more damage you do.
But, hey, you never know.
